{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/2555", "repo": "rails", "body": "I've \r\n* changed square brackets to the curly ones in column type definition (so zsh and bash are ok)\r\n* changed a dot to a comma\r\n* added ability to specify (uniq|unique) in column definition (instead of index)\r\n\r\nso now it's possible to write 'discount:decimal{5,2}:unique' or 'user_uuid:uniq' while generating new model/migration.\r\n\r\nWhat do you think of this? I'll investigate on this further tomorrow. Thanks.", "_id": {"$oid": "5238426bbd3543c151010b17"}, "issue_id": 2555, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/3264235", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/2555#issuecomment-3264235", "updated_at": "2011-12-23T20:03:11Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/german/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/german/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/german/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/german/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/german", "login": "german", "gravatar_id": "ac26c8df072a31865cf42e838fbdaa33", "html_url": "https://github.com/german", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/german/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/german/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/german/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/ac26c8df072a31865cf42e838fbdaa33?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F5d4c7bf4ebab441c07f4fa26c4f0c4c3.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/german/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 33149, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/german/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2011-12-23T20:02:52Z", "id": 3264235, "owner": "rails"}
